What you need to know:

Other appointees to the Premier League management committee are Western Stima chairman Laban Jobita, Elly Kalekwa (Sofapaka), Dan Shikanda (AFC Leopards), Robert Maoga (Kariobangi Sharks), Jon Terry (Posta Rangers), and Dennis Gicheru (Wazito).Meanwhile, David Thiru will be tasked with overseeing the league operations, while Grace Mwelu is the League's Communication and Marketing manager.